Unity Editor Live Capture Packages 2022 - 2023
The Live Capture package allows users to bring characters and cameras to life within the Unity Editor, leveraging Apple devices for natural motion capture. This eliminates the need for manually keyframing each movement or camera path, streamlining the animation process.

The Weta Realtime Tools for Unity editor enhance workflow efficiency and enable the creation of visually impressive content for both game and film production. This suite of features streamlines the development process, facilitating the rapid creation of high-quality visuals.
